    "Id": "575862",
    "ThreadId": "212417",
    "Html": "<p>This looks like a problem of the Culture-Property.</p>\r\n<p>But I could not found any Culture-Property.</p>\r\n<p>You can try the Language-Property:</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<div style=\"color: black; background-color: white;\">\r\n<pre>&lt;ContentControl Content=<span style=\"color: #a31515;\">\"{TemplateBinding DependentValue}\"</span> ContentStringFormat=<span style=\"color: #a31515;\">\"{} {0:C0}\"</span> Language=<span style=\"color: #a31515;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">en-GB</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">\"</span>/&gt;\r\n<span id=\"search\"></span></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</p>",
    "PostedDate": "2011-03-04T16:27:36.507-08:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
  },
  {
    "Id": "577110",
    "ThreadId": "212417",
    "Html": "<p>Good day!</p>\r\n<p>This problem can easily be solved by just going to tht&nbsp;stack panel&nbsp;and write \"xml:lang=\"en-GB\"\"</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;\"><font face=\"Consolas\" size=\"2\" color=\"#0000ff\">\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</font></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #a31515; font-size: x-small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Consolas; color: #a31515; font-size: x-small;\">&lt;StackPanel xml:lang=\"en-GB\"&gt;<br />&nbsp;&lt;ContentControl Content=\"{TemplateBinding DependentValue}\" <br />&nbsp;ContentStringFormat=\"{} {0:C0}\"/&gt;<br />&lt;/StackPanel&gt;<br />&nbsp;</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>",
